title: BRIEF-Kaps Investment raising its stake in TelForceOne to 50.34 pct
text:
BRIEF-Kaps Investment raising its stake in TelForceOne to 50.34 pct Sept 4 
Sept 4 TelForceOne SA : 
* Kaps Investment Sp. z o. o. acquires 445,001 company's shares, raising its stake to 50.34 percent from 44.9 percent
